{
  "id": "adv_main_04_03_02",
  "title": "星空編1章12話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――トリエルがサニピに敗北した、翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The day after TRINITYAiLE's defeat by Sunny Peace",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 1.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "久しぶりに恋愛映画を観てんけど、告白シーン\nめっちゃ良かったなあ、キュンキュンしたわ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's been a while since I watched a romantic movie‚ that confession scene\nwas so good‚ it made my heart went pit-a-pat~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "今日は誘ってくれてありがとう、いい気分転換になった\nけど……ほんまは琴乃ちゃんと来たかったんちゃう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for inviting me today. It was a nice change of pace\nHowever… you really wanted to come with Kotono-chan‚ didn't you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.147233073
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "違うよ！　琴乃ちゃんとはいつでもデート出来るもん\n今日は、優ちゃんとお喋りしたい気分だったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No! I can go on a date with Kotono-chan anytime\nToday‚ I was in the mood to chat with Yu-chan",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.7089562417
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "嬉しいなあ。……でも本当は、酷い負け方をして\n落ち込んでるうちを心配して声を掛けてくれたんやろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm so happy. …But the truth is‚ you were worried about me\nI was devastated by my terrible defeat‚ so you spoke to me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.5392966908
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……心配って言うより、応援したい感じかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Umm… it's more like I want to cheering you rather than worrying",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.5392966908,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "頑張ってるのに思うようにいかなくて辛い時期は\n私にもあったから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I also had tough time when things didn't go as planned\ndespite working hard",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.6060316564
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "その辛い時期を乗り越えてBIG4まで\n上り詰めた渚ちゃんは、ほんまに凄いわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nagisa-chan‚ you overcame those tough times and\nmade it to the BIG4‚ you're truly amazing",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.7967233658,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.4807484468
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "……泣き言言うのは好きちゃうけど\n今だけちょっと弱音吐いてもええかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I don't like to complain‚\nis it okay if I show a little weakness for a moment?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "いいよ。私で良ければなんでも聞くよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sure. If it's okay with you‚ I'll listen to anything",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.9517007351,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.9517007351
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 67.6687075298
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.6687075298
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "……ライブバトルが終わってからずっと\nなんでトリエルが負けたのか理由を考えてるんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…After live battle ended‚ I still\nwondering why TRINITYAiLE lost",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.2381632488
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "うちらに何が足りなかったんやろ……\nどこが悪かったんやろ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What did we lack…\nWhat was wrong…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.9748986256,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことばかり考えて……思ったんよ\nトリエルが負けたのは、うちのせいちゃうかなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was thinking about those things… something came to mind\nIt's my fault that TRINITYAiLE lost",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "どうしてそう思ったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why do you think that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.1595001857,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.1595001857
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.2231716871
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルは三人が助け合い、支え合って\n三人で並んで前に進むことで高く羽ばたくグループや",
      "translations": {
        "en": "TRINITYAiLE is a group of three who help each other‚ support each other‚\nand move forward together side by side‚ flapping their wings high",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.2999969482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "けど、うちはちゃんと支え合えていたんやろか？\n瑠依ちゃんの隣に並び立てていたんやろか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ was I supporting her properly?\nWas I standing next to Rui-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.8999954223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 109.7099730571
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "この前出た雑誌でも、瑠依ちゃんは「天才アイドル」\n「トリエルの絶対的センター」って紹介されてて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In a recent magazine‚ Rui-chan was introduced as a 'Genius idol'‚\n'The absolute center of TRINITYAiLE'…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.2333287556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.6630339067
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルの三人の中で瑠依ちゃんだけ突出して\n輝いていると思われてるんかなって、考えたりして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wonder if people think that Rui-chan is the only one\nwho stands out members of TRINITYAiLE…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.2333287556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 126.7834194899
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_meeting-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 130.7333287556
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "悪く考え過ぎだよ。優ちゃんもすみれちゃんも……\nトリエルは三人とも特別だって、みんな分かってるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're overthinking it. Also Yu-chan and Sumire-chan…\nEveryone knows that all three of TRINITYAiLE members are special",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.4333287556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 136.2524899881
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "優ちゃんは可愛くて茶目っ気があってトークが面白くて\nソロ写真集が話題になるくらいスタイルが良くて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu-chan is cute and playful‚ so talk is fun\nStyle is so good that solo photo album became a hot topic…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.8999954223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 149.4999954223
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん他の二人にも素敵なところが沢山あって……\nそんな三人が支え合って輝くからトリエルは凄いんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ the other two also have many good points…\nTRINITYAiLE is amazing because these three support each other and shine",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.4999954223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 154.4753243209
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "うちもずっとそう思ってた……\nけど、一番注目を浴びるのはやっぱりセンターやんか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've always thought that way too…\nHowever‚ the center is the one who attracts the most attention",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.366662089,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02-yu014.m4a",
      "text": "BIG4に果敢に挑むうちらへの\n世間の期待や好奇の視線は尋常やない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For us‚ eagerly challenging the BIG4‚\nthe world's expectations and curious gazes are no small thing",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.2666631062,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
