      "text": "そんな押しつぶされそうな重圧を、瑠依ちゃんはいつも\nセンターとして一身に受け止めてくれていた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui-chan always took on that crushing pressure\nwith her whole body as the center",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.866662089,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
