      "text": "うちがセンターの瑠依ちゃんを支えなあかんのに\n実際はうちが瑠依ちゃんにずっと守られていたんや",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have to support the center‚ Rui-chan‚\nbut truth is‚ I've been protected by Rui-chan the whole time",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.266662089,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
