      "text": "不甲斐ない話やわ……うちにもっと実力があれば\n瑠依ちゃん一人にここまで重荷を背負わせんかったのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's a shameful story… If I had more skills‚\nRui-chan wouldn't have had to carry such a heavy burden all by herself",
        "id": ""
