      "text": "気持ちは分かるよ。私もセンターを……琴乃ちゃんを\n支えているつもりで、無意識に甘えて、頼っていたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand how you feel. I thought I was also supporting the center… Kotono-chan\nso I unconsciously hoped for help and relied on her",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 200.366662089,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
