      },
      "startTime": 369.7333328246,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "私はもともとは子役をしていて、仕事がなくなって……\nアイドルに転身するために養成所に入ったから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was originally a child actor‚ but I lost my job…\nI entered training school to become an idol…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 379.3541888038,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃんや優ちゃんみたいに、一からアイドルを\n目指していた人とは違うのかなって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought it it was different from people like Rui-chan or Yu-chan‚\nwho had their goal from the beginning to be idols…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 386.8333328246,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "確かすみれは、バンプロの養成所で\n瑠依さん達と知り合ったのでしたわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sumire met Rui-san and Yu-san\nat the Van Prods. training school",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 393.8666661579,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_flashback-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 400.9666661579
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "うん……養成所に通い始めてすぐ\n基礎も出来てない私に、瑠依ちゃんは言ってくれたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… As soon as I started training school‚\nRui-chan told me that I couldn't even do the basics",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 401.3333328246,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "あなたは私達にはないものを……\nあなたにしかないものを持っている、って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You have what we don't have…\nYou have what only you‚ have",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 409.4666661579,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "子役として生き残れなくて、私はその他大勢の中に\n埋もれていったから……そう言われて嬉しかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I couldn't survive as a child actor‚ and got lost\nin the crowd… so I was so happy to hear that",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 418.3000005085,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "あなたにしかない、あなただけの輝くものがあるって\n……その言葉が本当に嬉しかったんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's something that shines only for you‚ something that only for you\n…Those words really made me happy",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 428.5666661579,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "その後すみれは、瑠依さんや優と組むことになって\nトリエルとしてデビューしたのですわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After that‚ Sumire teamed up with Rui-san and Yu-san‚\nand debuted as TRINITYAiLE",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 436.2999994913,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02-smr015.m4a",
      "text": "うん……だから期待に応えなきゃって思った\n私が二人の足を引っ張る訳にはいかないから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… so I thought I had to live up to expectations\nI couldn't hold them back",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 444.7999994913,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_serious-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 449.1333328246
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02-smr016.m4a",
      "text": "でもこんなに必死に頑張って、限界を超えて努力しても\nサニピにはまるで届かなかった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But no matter how desperately I tried‚ how hard I pushed myself‚\nI couldn't reach Sunny Peace…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 455.7333328246,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02-smr017.m4a",
      "text": "私じゃここが限界なのかな？\nやっぱり私はアイドルに向いてないのかな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe this is my limit?\nMaybe I'm not cut out to be an idol after all…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 462.8999994913,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "一つ質問してもよろしいかしら？\nすみれはアイドルのお仕事が好きなんですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Can I ask you a question?\nDo you like being an idol‚ Sumire?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 471.5999994913,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02-smr018.m4a",
      "text": "……好きだよ\n瑠依ちゃんと歌うのも、優ちゃんと踊るのも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I love it.\nSinging with Rui-chan‚ dancing with Yu-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 478.0666661579,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_happy-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 482.1315365549
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02-smr019.m4a",
      "text": "ペンライトの光も……ファンのみんなの声援も……\n私の歌でみんなが笑顔になるのも、大好きだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Light of the penlights… and the cheers of the fans…\nI also really love how my songs make everyone smile",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 486.7333328246,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "その気持ちがあるのなら\nアイドルに向いてないなんてことはありませんわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you feel that way‚\nthere's no way you're not cut out to be an idol",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 494.2666661579,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "苦しい時でもアイドルが好きで、ファンの人達が好きで\n続けたいと思ってる。それだけで立派なアイドルです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even when times are tough‚ you still love idols‚ you still love your fans‚\nand you want to continue. That alone makes you a great idol",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 502.5666661579,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "胸を張りなさい！　自信を持ちなさい！　誰がなんと\n言おうと、奥山すみれは素晴らしいアイドルですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hold your head high! Have confidence! No matter what\nanyone says‚ Sumire Okuyama is a great idol!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 513.3666661579,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02-smr020.m4a",
      "text": "ああ……すずちゃん……ありがとう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahh… Suzu-chan… thank you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 518.5527839419,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02-smr021.m4a",
      "text": "そっか……私はアイドルでいていいんだ……\nトリエルにいていいんだ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So… I'm fine with being an idol…\nI'm fine with being TRINITYAiLE…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 530.1333328246,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02-smr022.m4a",
      "text": "すずちゃんは凄いなあ、一言言われただけで\n暗い気持ちが吹っ飛んじゃったよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu-chan is amazing‚ just hearing one word\nmade all my gloomy feelings blew away…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 536.5666661579,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02-smr023.m4a",
      "text": "すずちゃん、相談に乗ってくれてありがとう\nすずちゃんは頼りになるお姉ちゃんだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu-chan‚ thank you for your advice\nSuzu-chan is reliable one-san",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 543.8848474076,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_02-suz014.m4a",
      "text": "このぐらいどうということはありませんわ\n困った時はお姉さんの私にいつでも相談なさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's no need to say anything about this\nIf you have any trouble‚ please feel free to consult me‚ your one-san",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 551.1666661579,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}